**Content:** This isn't about replacing great teachers; it's about expanding access to them. How many students can afford small, intimate classes with top-tier instructors?  Online learning allows us to bring elements of that experience to a wider audience.  The flexibility of online learning also benefits research. Removing geographical constraints allows researchers more time in the field and access to global resources.
